headline: Assessing Brown & Brown (BRO) Valuation After Recent Share Price Weakness
summary: Recent share performance and business profile Brown & Brown (BRO) has drawn fresh attention after recent trading left the shares with a return of about 0.7% over the past day, while showing negative moves over the past week and month. Over the past 3 months, the stock has recorded a return of about a 9.8% decline, and about a 24.8% decline over the past year, leading some investors to reassess the insurance broker’s longer term record and current fundamentals.
